<h1 style="text-align: center;">Welcome to the Downtown Brown Ice Rink!</h1>
<br />

<!-- Who we are -->
<p class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-3 bg-info" style="border: 1px dashed black;" >
    <b><u>Who we are</u></b>
    <br />
    Downtown Brown ice rink was established in 2017 and has already become one of the
    most popular rinks and shops in all of North America. We have multiple <b>hockey teams</b>
    from all divisions and age ranges, along with <b>figure skating, public skate, and 
    new this year is curling!</b>
</p>

