    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Monday to Friday -> 12pm-1:30pm <br />
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Saturday and Sunday -> 12pm-2pm and 6pm-8pm <br />
    <i>Learn to skate:</i><br />
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Saturday -> 2pm-4pm <br />
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Sunday -> 2pm-3:30pm <br />
    <i>High School Hockey:</i><br />
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Monday, Wednesday, Friday -> 6pm-9pm<br />
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Thursday and Saturday -> 5pm-9pm<br />
    <i>College Hockey:</i><br />
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Monday to Friday -> 2pm-6pm<br />
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Saturday and Sunday -> 9am-12pm<br />
    <i>Open Hockey:</i><br />
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Every Day -> 10pm-12am<br />
</p>
